A=(a_{ij}) \in \mathbb C^{n\times n}
\rho(A) \leq \max_i\sum_j^n | a_{ij}|
\rho(A)
|\cdot|
\lambda
\exists i, |\lambda - a_{ii}| \leq \sum_{j\neq i} |a_{ij}|
|\lambda - a_{ii}| \geq |\lambda| - |a_{ii}|
|\lambda| - |a_{ii}| \leq \sum_{j\neq i} |a_{ij}|.
|\lambda| \leq \sum_{j} |a_{ij}| \leq \max_{i} \sum_{j} |a_{ij}|.
